│ 231                                    2 * SCEVCheapExpansionBudget, TTI,     │
│ PHTerm) ||                                                                    │
│ 232       !Rewriter.isSafeToExpandAt(InvariantLHS, PHTerm) ||                 │
│ 233       !Rewriter.isSafeToExpandAt(InvariantRHS, PHTerm))                   │
